servers.description: Sets the server blacklist. Each entry can be a list of servers separated by comma in the format: servicehost:portservicehost2:portservicehost3:port

properties.description: Set client properties to use. These properties are specific to what service call implementation are in use. For example if using ribbon then the client properties are define in com.netflix.client.config.CommonClientConfigKey.

id.description: Sets the value of the id property.
